RelatedSentence: KARACHI : An anti-terrorism court on Saturday ordered the release of a suspect in the Tahir Plaza arson attack case for want of evidence against him .
Police submitted that he was arrested in other cases and disclosed his involvement in the present case during interrogations by a joint investigation team .
